{"product_id":"zima-go","title":"Zima UV Case","description":"\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMost retainer \u0026amp; aligner cases are low quality, poorly designed and fail to consider the risks caused by dangerous microorganisms that build up on your appliance.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Zima UV Case is a sleek, metal case with a smooth sliding lid mechanism and integrated Ultraviolet (UV) sanitisation technology to remove bacteria on the go.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEliminate bacteria, viruses and pathogens on the go\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEnjoy a premium and protective metal finish\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEasily fit your appliance with increased capacity\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStay discreet with a sleek sliding lid mechanism\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"ZIMA Dental UK","offers":[{"title":"Silver","offer_id":48686430355733,"sku":"ZCV-SLV-EU","price":79.99,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Rose Gold","offer_id":49402847068437,"sku":"ZCV-RGD-EU","price":79.99,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Matte Black","offer_id":48686430388501,"sku":"ZCV-BLK-EU","price":89.99,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0699\/9569\/2309\/files\/Zima_Go_Silver_OPEN_-_UV_Purple_Glow_sq.webp?v=1774327540","url":"https:\/\/zimadental.nl\/products\/zima-go","provider":"ZIMA DENTAL EU","version":"1.0","type":"link"}